793
00:43:54.221 --> 00:43:57.428
Oh, he's taping another TV commercial,
but you can wait in his office.


794
00:43:58.123 --> 00:43:59.884
-Thank you.
-You're very welcome.


795
00:44:03.019 --> 00:44:05.406
Hamilton Realty. Hi, Amy.

