925
00:50:22.448 --> 00:50:24.827
and I always thought he was cuter
without his glasses, so...


926
00:50:25.284 --> 00:50:26.702
one day he took them off for me.

927
00:50:27.841 --> 00:50:30.541
And he slipped on the ice,
and fell right on his fanny.


928
00:50:31.470 --> 00:50:32.779
Sounds like love to me.

929
00:50:34.437 --> 00:50:36.076
Daddy said we were born friends.

930
00:50:39.876 --> 00:50:41.505
He did a lot for Henry, your father.

931
00:50:42.415 --> 00:50:43.419
He was the best.

932
00:50:44.483 --> 00:50:47.245
