♪ We all want
our voices to be heard

1614
01:27:01.722 --> 01:27:04.454
♪ Everyone

1615
01:27:04.744 --> 01:27:08.556
♪ Wants a chance to be someone

1616
01:27:09.160 --> 01:27:12.859
♪ We all have
dreams we need to dream

1617
01:27:13.446 --> 01:27:17.904
♪ Sweeter than any star you can reach

1618
01:27:17.965 --> 01:27:21.765
♪ 'Cause when you reach and find

1619
01:27:22.121 --> 01:27:25.638
♪ You've found someone

1620
01:27:26.004 --> 01:27:30.031
♪ You'll hold this world's
most priceless thing


1621
01:27:30.269 --> 01:27:34.249
♪ The greatest gift this life can bring

1622
01:27:34.310 --> 01:27:38.179
♪ Is when you look back and know

1623
01:27:38.464 --> 01:27:41.956
♪ You were loved ♪

1624
01:27:56.335 --> 01:27:59.820
Oh, Keeleys... 
Take a left at Woodlawn.

