The Keeleys live on Sixth.

1626
01:28:02.928 --> 01:28:06.114
Henry, the Keeleys live on Woodlawn.

1627
01:28:08.734 --> 01:28:09.465
You're jealous.

1628
01:28:10.095 --> 01:28:11.223
I am not jealous.

1629
01:28:11.284 --> 01:28:12.069
Yes, you are.

1630
01:28:12.204 --> 01:28:14.619
I may be a lot of things, but
jealous is not one of them.


1631
01:28:14.694 --> 01:28:15.510
Sure, you are.

1632
01:28:15.809 --> 01:28:17.530
You're so jealous, you
can't even think straight.


1633
01:28:17.591 --> 01:28:19.957
I am thinking just fine, thank you.

1634
01:28:20.310 --> 01:28:22.158
You can't even remember
where the Keeleys live.


1635
01:28:22.219 --> 01:28:23.919
The Keeleys' house is on Sixth.

1636
01:28:23.980 --> 01:28:25.892
-Then what's it doing over there?
-What?


1637
01:28:27.746 --> 01:28:28.333
Hmm.

1638
01:28:32.785 --> 01:28:33.765
Keeleys moved.

1639
01:28:35.240 --> 01:28:37.048
Woodlawn. Sixth.

1640
01:28:38.143 --> 01:28:39.153
Is this it?

1641
01:28:39.463 --> 01:28:41.715
Mm-hmm. There's the house.

1642
01:28:41.960 --> 01:28:43.773
-Be careful, Henry.
-I will be.


1643
01:28:44.803 --> 01:28:47.526
Drive all this way,
they're probably not even home.


1644
01:28:51.220 --> 01:28:53.072
At least they could
shovel their walkway.


1645
01:28:54.813 --> 01:28:55.757
Whoooaaah!

1646
01:29:04.208 --> 01:29:05.083
Henry!

1647
01:29:08.246 --> 01:29:09.692
What are you laughin' at?

1648
01:29:12.003 --> 01:29:14.643
You look like a kid. 
Are you all right?

1649
01:29:14.717 --> 01:29:17.303
-I'm fine.
-Let me help you up.


1650
01:29:17.548 --> 01:29:18.437
Thanks, babe.

1651
01:29:20.615 --> 01:29:23.205
Oh, baby. What are you doing?

1652
01:29:23.266 --> 01:29:26.001
-I thought you was helpin' me up.
-You did this on purpose.


1653
01:29:28.333 --> 01:29:30.140
Eddie, come here quick.
It's the preacher.


1654
01:29:30.415 --> 01:29:33.722
-What's goin' on?
-I hope you didn't hurt yourself.


1655
01:29:34.364 --> 01:29:36.689
-You all right?
-We're fine.


1656
01:29:36.750 --> 01:29:38.127
I told these kids to shovel that walk.

1657
01:29:38.188 --> 01:29:40.952
They ain't got nothin' on their mind
but Santa Claus. Sorry.


1658
01:29:42.285 --> 01:29:43.860
-This is yours. Merry Christmas.
-Us?


1659
01:29:44.094 --> 01:29:46.924
-Merry Christmas.
-God bless you.


1660
01:29:48.375 --> 01:29:50.463
-You'll catch cold. Be careful.
-We will.


1661
01:29:50.860 --> 01:29:51.695
I'll see you on Sunday.

1662
01:29:51.756 --> 01:29:53.624
We'll be there. All of us.

1663
01:29:57.754 --> 01:30:00.044
Seems like we've been
doin' this forever.


1664
01:30:00.340 --> 01:30:02.863
Forever is right.
Do you remember the first time?


1665
01:30:04.361 --> 01:30:05.890
-My mother was visiting, yeah.
-Yes.


1666
01:30:07.451 --> 01:30:10.615
-You know, Henry, she never liked me.
-No, no, that's not true.


1667
01:30:10.676 --> 01:30:13.735
She used to say, 'Girl, you better
get some meat on them there bones.'


1668
01:30:15.698 --> 01:30:17.366
Well, she just wanted
you to eat, that's all.


1669
01:30:17.427 --> 01:30:21.065
-No, she wanted me to be as fat as her.
-She wasn't that fat.


1670
01:30:21.126 --> 01:30:24.225
Henry, a policeman walk down the street,
see your mama and go, 'Break it up!'


1671
01:30:26.586 --> 01:30:27.272
Stop!

1672
01:30:29.240 --> 01:30:30.418
Stop it!

1673
01:30:31.361 --> 01:30:32.311
Rest her soul.

1674
01:30:35.240 --> 01:30:36.624
It's good to see you laugh again.

1675
01:30:39.529 --> 01:30:40.962
It's nice to have a reason to.

1676
01:30:43.547 --> 01:30:46.088
You know, I miss this Henry.

1677
01:30:48.327 --> 01:30:50.137
I wish he'd show up more often.

1678
01:31:04.092 --> 01:31:05.967
There. We did it.

1679
01:31:08.804 --> 01:31:11.776
I'm gonna go to the church for a minute.
You go on inside.


1680
01:31:20.049 --> 01:31:21.880
-There we go.
-Thank you.


1681
01:31:22.985 --> 01:31:24.075
Don't slip.

1682
01:31:25.425 --> 01:31:26.811
I won't. Don't be long.

